Solidity Tutorials
-----------------------
Use remix to code. Solidity is the programming langage.
Solidity source file -> Solidity Compiler(solc(c++ lib), solcjs(node lib)) -> ABI(Abstract Binanry Interface) + Contract Bytecode
ABI -> Responsible for API that gets trigger from outside client.
Contract Bytecode gets deployed in EVM(Ethereum Virtual Machine)

Solidity contract must have license.
// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later

Sample contract
// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later

pragma solidity 0.8.16;

contract Property{
    
    int public value;

    function setValue(int _value) public {
        value=_value;
    }
}
